### 8.2 Timing Accuracy Analysis

**TDOA Precision Derivation:**

Za cross-korelacijski estimator TDOA, CramÃ©r-Rao Lower Bound (CRLB) je:

$$\sigma_{TDOA} = \frac{1}{2\pi \cdot B_{eff} \cdot \sqrt{SNR \cdot T_{int}}}$$

Gdje je:
- $B_{eff}$ = efektivna Å¡irina pojasa (~100 MHz)
- $SNR$ = omjer signal/Å¡um
- $T_{int}$ = vrijeme integracije

**NumeriÄki primjer:**

| Parametar | Vrijednost |
|-----------|------------|
| $B_{eff}$ | 100 MHz |
| $SNR$ | 20 dB (100 linearno) |
| $T_{int}$ | 1 s |

$$\sigma_{TDOA} = \frac{1}{2\pi \cdot 10^8 \cdot \sqrt{100 \cdot 1}} = \frac{1}{6.28 \cdot 10^8 \cdot 10} = 0.16 \text{ ns}$$

**To odgovara prostornoj rezoluciji:**
$$\sigma_{range} = c \cdot \sigma_{TDOA} = 3 \times 10^8 \cdot 0.16 \times 10^{-9} = 48 \text{ mm}$$

---

## 9. TDOA Geolocation Algorithm

